x.ssf/2017/09/shooting_reported_at_freeman_h.html|newspaper=Oregon Live|agency=Associated Press|date=September 13, 2017|accessdate=September 13, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|September 20, 2017}}\n|[[Mattoon, Illinois]], US\n| Student \n| \n| 1 injured\n| [[Mattoon High School]]: A 14-year-old male student was subdued by a female teacher when he attempted to open fire in the school cafeteria at 11:33&nbsp;a.m. Multiple shots were fired in the process, and one student was struck in the chest. The victims was driven to a nearby hospital suffering non-life-threatening wounds. The suspect was taken into custody without further incident.<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.mattoon.k12.il.us/vnews/display.v/ART/59c2b2193096f |title = Mattoon Community Unit School District 2 \u2013 MHS students, staff secure following shooting |website= www.mattoon.k12.il.us |language = en |access-date = September 21, 2017 |url-status = live |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144403/https://www.mattoon.k12.il.us/vnews/display.v/ART/59c2b2193096f |archivedate = September 21, 2017 |df = mdy-all }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://time.com/4950377/mattoon-illinois-high-school-shooting/ |title = Suspect in Custody After Injuring One in Shooting at Illinois High School |last = Press |first = Associated |website= Time |access-date = September 21, 2017 |url-status = dead |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920231817/http://time.com/4950377/mattoon-illinois-high-school-shooting/ |archivedate = September 20, 2017 |df = mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|September 26, 2017}}\n|[[Bronx, New York]], US \n| Student \n| 1 dead\n| 1 injured\n| Abel Cedeno killing incident. A 15-year-old student was stabbed to death and a 16-year-old was critically injured at Urban Assembly School for Wildlife Conservation, a grades 6-12 school. An 18-year-old student was charged with murder. It was speculated that the suspect was bothered by the victims' homophobic comments.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www